item.title: Wierd Log in Error
item.dc:creator: @DRAGON_GIRL DRAGON GIRL
item.description:
@DRAGON_GIRL wrote:

go to control panel
switch to category view
click windows firewall
click exceptions
click add port
type RSPS for PORT NAME
type 43594 for PORT NUMBER
AND YOU PORTFORWARDED
i had to do that cause i have 2-wire 2701HG-B
